      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "陈文古上。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03091008_e00002",
      "play_id": "03091008",
      "scene_id": "03091008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 2,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "陈文古"
      ],
      "text": "斩草不除根，萌芽依旧生。斩草要去根，萌芽永不生。",
      "text_length": 24
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03091008_e00003",
      "play_id": "03091008",
      "scene_id": "03091008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 3,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "陈文古"
      ],
      "text": "在下、陈文古。我有一好友名叫奎文吉，他家有一宝物，名叫瑞霓罗帐，是我叫他价卖与我，他执意不肯，因此我用酒将他劝醉，将短刀、银两藏在他的身边，推往大街之上，被那巡更之人拿走，当他偷盗杀人，送往公堂，苦打成招，问成死罪。他妻子骂上我门，是我用计，以石灰将她眼目揉瞎，打入磨房，又将他子奎顺打入那马房。",
      "text_length": 148
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03091008_e00004",
      "play_id": "03091008",
      "scene_id": "03091008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 4,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "陈碧桃暗上，偷听。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03091008_e00005",
      "play_id": "03091008",
      "scene_id": "03091008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 5,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "陈文古"
      ],
      "text": "我想这一不做二不休，不免叫老家院陈荣于三更时分去到马房，将奎顺一刀刺死！",
      "text_length": 36
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03091008_e00006",
      "play_id": "03091008",
      "scene_id": "03091008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 6,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "陈碧桃下。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03091008_e00007",
      "play_id": "03091008",
      "scene_id": "03091008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 7,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "陈文古"
      ],
      "text": "岂不是没有后患了么！就是这个主意。陈荣哪里！",
      "text_length": 22
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03091008_e00008",
      "play_id": "03091008",
      "scene_id": "03091008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 8,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "陈荣上。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03091008_e00009",
      "play_id": "03091008",
      "scene_id": "03091008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 9,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "引子",
      "speakers": [
        "陈荣"
      ],
      "text": "老迈年高，叹光阴，何时得了！",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03091008_e00010",
      "play_id": "03091008",
      "scene_id": "03091008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 10,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "陈荣"
      ],
      "text": "老汉、陈荣。正在后面检点，大爷呼唤，只得近前。大爷在上，老奴叩头！",
      "text_length": 33
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03091008_e00011",
      "play_id": "03091008",
      "scene_id": "03091008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 11,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "陈文古"
      ],
      "text": "站起来！",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03091008_e00012",
      "play_id": "03091008",
      "scene_id": "03091008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 12,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "陈荣"
      ],
      "text": "谢大爷！",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03091008_e00013",
      "play_id": "03091008",
      "scene_id": "03091008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 13,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "陈文古"
      ],
      "text": "看茶来！",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03091008_e00014",
      "play_id": "03091008",
      "scene_id": "03091008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 14,
      "seq_in_scene": 14,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "陈荣"
      ],
      "text": "是。",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03091008_e00015",
      "play_id": "03091008",
      "scene_id": "03091008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 15,
      "seq_in_scene": 15,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "陈荣取茶。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03091008_e00016",
      "play_id": "03091008",
      "scene_id": "03091008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 16,
      "seq_in_scene": 16,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "陈荣"
      ],
      "text": "大爷请茶。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03091008_e00017",
      "play_id": "03091008",
      "scene_id": "03091008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 17,
      "seq_in_scene": 17,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "陈文古取杯饮，取银放杯内。",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03091008_e00018",
      "play_id": "03091008",
      "scene_id": "03091008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 18,
      "seq_in_scene": 18,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "陈文古"
      ],
      "text": "接杯。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03091008_e00019",
      "play_id": "03091008",
      "scene_id": "03091008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 19,
      "seq_in_scene": 19,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "陈荣接杯，看。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03091008_e00020",
      "play_id": "03091008",
      "scene_id": "03091008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 20,
      "seq_in_scene": 20,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "陈荣"
      ],
      "text": "呀，杯内有白银一锭，是何缘故？待我收下，他有来言，我有去语。",
      "text_length": 30
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03091008_e00021",
      "play_id": "03091008",
      "scene_id": "03091008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 21,
      "seq_in_scene": 21,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "陈文古"
      ],
      "text": "陈荣，杯内可有什么？",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03091008_e00022",
      "play_id": "03091008",
      "scene_id": "03091008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 22,
      "seq_in_scene": 22,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "陈荣"
      ],
      "text": "只见白银一锭，是老奴收下了。",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03091008_e00023",
      "play_id": "03091008",
      "scene_id": "03091008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 23,
      "seq_in_scene": 23,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "陈文古"
      ],
      "text": "赏与你的。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03091008_e00024",
      "play_id": "03091008",
      "scene_id": "03091008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 24,
      "seq_in_scene": 24,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "陈荣"
      ],
      "text": "谢大爷！",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03091008_e00025",
      "play_id": "03091008",
      "scene_id": "03091008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 25,
      "seq_in_scene": 25,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "陈文古"
      ],
      "text": "陈荣，大爷待你如何？",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03091008_e00026",
      "play_id": "03091008",
      "scene_id": "03091008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 26,
      "seq_in_scene": 26,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "陈荣"
      ],
      "text": "大爷待小人恩重如山。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03091008_e00027",
      "play_id": "03091008",
      "scene_id": "03091008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 27,
      "seq_in_scene": 27,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "陈文古"
      ],
      "text": "我有桩心事要你去办，你可愿去？",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03091008_e00028",
      "play_id": "03091008",
      "scene_id": "03091008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 28,
      "seq_in_scene": 28,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "陈荣"
      ],
      "text": "只要去得的，老奴焉敢不去！",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03091008_e00029",
      "play_id": "03091008",
      "scene_id": "03091008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 29,
      "seq_in_scene": 29,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "陈文古"
      ],
      "text": "命你三更时分，去到马房，将奎顺一刀刺死！",
      "text_length": 20
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03091008_e00030",
      "play_id": "03091008",
      "scene_id": "03091008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 30,
      "seq_in_scene": 30,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "陈荣"
      ],
      "text": "哎呀，大爷！杀人之事，老奴不敢去！",
      "text_length": 17
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03091008_e00031",
      "play_id": "03091008",
      "scene_id": "03091008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 31,
      "seq_in_scene": 31,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "陈文古"
      ],
      "text": "住口！胆大的狗才，叫你走东不敢到西。你若不去，活活打死你这老狗！",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03091008_e00032",
      "play_id": "03091008",
      "scene_id": "03091008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 32,
      "seq_in_scene": 32,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "陈荣"
      ],
      "text": "哎呀！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03091008_e00033",
      "play_id": "03091008",
      "scene_id": "03091008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 33,
      "seq_in_scene": 33,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "陈荣背供。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03091008_e00034",
      "play_id": "03091008",
      "scene_id": "03091008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 34,
      "seq_in_scene": 34,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "陈荣"
      ],
      "text": "我老糊涂了，此番去到马房，杀也在我，不杀也在我。嗯，自有道理。",
      "text_length": 31
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03091008_e00035",
      "play_id": "03091008",
      "scene_id": "03091008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 35,
      "seq_in_scene": 35,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "陈荣向陈文古。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03091008_e00036",
      "play_id": "03091008",
      "scene_id": "03091008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 36,
      "seq_in_scene": 36,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "陈荣"
      ],
      "text": "大爷，老奴愿去，只是无有利器。",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03091008_e00037",
      "play_id": "03091008",
      "scene_id": "03091008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 37,
      "seq_in_scene": 37,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "陈文古"
      ],
      "text": "随我来！这有钢刀一把，杀了奎顺，方可见我；杀不了奎顺，死也不要见我！去吧！",
      "text_length": 37
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03091008_e00038",
      "play_id": "03091008",
      "scene_id": "03091008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 38,
      "seq_in_scene": 38,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "陈文古下。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03091008_e00039",
      "play_id": "03091008",
      "scene_id": "03091008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 39,
      "seq_in_scene": 39,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "陈荣"
      ],
      "text": "陈文古，好贼子啊！",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03091008_e00040",
      "play_id": "03091008",
      "scene_id": "03091008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 40,
      "seq_in_scene": 40,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "陈荣"
      ],
      "text": "陈文古做事心忒狠，暗害好友丧良心。朋友的妻儿你要个个杀尽，我岂肯为虎作伥做罪人！",
      "text_length": 40
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03091008_e00041",
      "play_id": "03091008",
      "scene_id": "03091008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 41,
      "seq_in_scene": 41,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "陈荣下。陈碧桃上。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03091008_e00042",
      "play_id": "03091008",
      "scene_id": "03091008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 42,
      "seq_in_scene": 42,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "陈碧桃"
      ],
      "text": "屏风后面听言讲，父亲为何把人伤！",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03091008_e00043",
      "play_id": "03091008",
      "scene_id": "03091008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 43,
      "seq_in_scene": 43,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "陈碧桃"
      ],
      "text": "奴家、陈碧桃。在屏风后听爹爹呼唤陈荣，命他三更时分去到马房，将奎家二相公一刀刺杀，我不免挡住宅门，候陈荣到来，问个明白。",
      "text_length": 60
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03091008_e00044",
      "play_id": "03091008",
      "scene_id": "03091008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 44,
      "seq_in_scene": 44,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "陈碧桃"
      ],
      "text": "可叹我母去世早，撇下女儿受煎熬。爹爹行事太可恼，要害奎顺为哪条？我既知情救为妙，不然一命赴阴曹。将身站此宅门道，等候陈荣问根苗。",
      "text_length": 64
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03091008_e00045",
      "play_id": "03091008",
      "scene_id": "03091008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 45,
      "seq_in_scene": 45,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "内白",
      "speakers": [
        "陈荣"
      ],
      "text": "走哇！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03091008_e00046",
      "play_id": "03091008",
      "scene_id": "03091008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 46,
      "seq_in_scene": 46,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "陈荣上。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03091008_e00047",
      "play_id": "03091008",
      "scene_id": "03091008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 47,
      "seq_in_scene": 47,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "陈碧桃"
      ],
      "text": "老院公转来！",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03091008_e00048",
      "play_id": "03091008",
      "scene_id": "03091008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 48,
      "seq_in_scene": 48,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "陈荣"
      ],
      "text": "什么人？",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03091008_e00049",
      "play_id": "03091008",
      "scene_id": "03091008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 49,
      "seq_in_scene": 49,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "陈碧桃"
      ],
      "text": "院公！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03091008_e00050",
      "play_id": "03091008",
      "scene_id": "03091008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 50,
      "seq_in_scene": 50,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "陈荣"
      ],
      "text": "原来是小姐。老奴叩头！",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03091008_e00051",
      "play_id": "03091008",
      "scene_id": "03091008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 51,
      "seq_in_scene": 51,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "陈碧桃"
      ],
      "text": "站起来。夜静更深，你往哪里去？",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03091008_e00052",
      "play_id": "03091008",
      "scene_id": "03091008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 52,
      "seq_in_scene": 52,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "陈荣"
      ],
      "text": "老奴奉了大爷之命，前后检点。",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03091008_e00053",
      "play_id": "03091008",
      "scene_id": "03091008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 53,
      "seq_in_scene": 53,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "陈碧桃"
      ],
      "text": "哪里是前后检点，分明奉了我爹爹之命，去到马房，将奎顺二相公一刀刺杀，是与不是？",
      "text_length": 39
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03091008_e00054",
      "play_id": "03091008",
      "scene_id": "03091008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 54,
      "seq_in_scene": 54,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "陈荣"
      ],
      "text": "小姑娘，老奴心事却被你猜着了！",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03091008_e00055",
      "play_id": "03091008",
      "scene_id": "03091008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 55,
      "seq_in_scene": 55,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "陈碧桃"
      ],
      "text": "老哥偌大年纪，为何这样世事不懂？",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03091008_e00056",
      "play_id": "03091008",
      "scene_id": "03091008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 56,
      "seq_in_scene": 56,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "陈荣"
      ],
      "text": "老奴也是无可奈何。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03091008_e00057",
      "play_id": "03091008",
      "scene_id": "03091008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 57,
      "seq_in_scene": 57,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "陈碧桃"
      ],
      "text": "老哥，这有银子一锭，去到马房，杀也在你，不杀也在你。",
      "text_length": 26
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03091008_e00058",
      "play_id": "03091008",
      "scene_id": "03091008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 58,
      "seq_in_scene": 58,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "陈荣"
      ],
      "text": "谢小姐！",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03091008_e00059",
      "play_id": "03091008",
      "scene_id": "03091008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 59,
      "seq_in_scene": 59,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "陈碧桃"
      ],
      "text": "偌大年纪，你是懂事人哪！",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03091008_e00060",
      "play_id": "03091008",
      "scene_id": "03091008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 60,
      "seq_in_scene": 60,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "陈碧桃下。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03091008_e00061",
      "play_id": "03091008",
      "scene_id": "03091008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 61,
      "seq_in_scene": 61,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "陈荣"
      ],
      "text": "小姐，哎呀，小姐呀！",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03091008_e00062",
      "play_id": "03091008",
      "scene_id": "03091008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 62,
      "seq_in_scene": 62,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "陈荣"
      ],
      "text": "好一个贤德陈小姐，他比陈荣胜十分。这样女子世间少，后来必定是贵人。",
      "text_length": 33
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03091008_e00063",
      "play_id": "03091008",
      "scene_id": "03091008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 63,
      "seq_in_scene": 63,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "陈荣下。奎顺上。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03091008_e00064",
      "play_id": "03091008",
      "scene_id": "03091008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 64,
      "seq_in_scene": 64,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "奎顺"
      ],
      "text": "泪似湘江水，滚滚不住流。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03091008_e00065",
      "play_id": "03091008",
      "scene_id": "03091008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 65,
      "seq_in_scene": 65,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "奎顺"
      ],
      "text": "小生、奎顺。只为瑞霓罗帐，陈文古将我父亲害在监中，老母打入磨房，好不气杀我也！",
      "text_length": 39
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03091008_e00066",
      "play_id": "03091008",
      "scene_id": "03091008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 66,
      "seq_in_scene": 66,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "奎顺"
      ],
      "text": "一霎时急得我三魂不在，七魂悠悠又转来。恨贼子来把我害，冤仇何日才得解开！",
      "text_length": 36
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03091008_e00067",
      "play_id": "03091008",
      "scene_id": "03091008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 67,
      "seq_in_scene": 67,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "陈荣上。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03091008_e00068",
      "play_id": "03091008",
      "scene_id": "03091008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 68,
      "seq_in_scene": 68,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "陈荣"
      ],
      "text": "急急忙忙把马房找，耳听谯楼二鼓敲。黄犬不住高声叫，狂风一阵灭灯苗。黑夜间观不见路途道，房内不见小儿曹。是何人把这风走了，陈文古知道怎肯饶！东廊不见西廊去找，他一觉睡着静悄悄。",
      "text_length": 87
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03091008_e00069",
      "play_id": "03091008",
      "scene_id": "03091008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 69,
      "seq_in_scene": 69,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "陈荣"
      ],
      "text": "啊，看奎家二相公，竟此睡着了！也罢，待我老汉惊醒于他。二相公有人行刺于你！",
      "text_length": 37
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03091008_e00070",
      "play_id": "03091008",
      "scene_id": "03091008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 70,
      "seq_in_scene": 70,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "奎顺"
      ],
      "text": "听一言来魂魄掉，跪在尘埃求命饶。有恩须当恩来报，无仇杀我为哪条？望求开恩释放了，结草衔环报恩高。",
      "text_length": 48
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03091008_e00071",
      "play_id": "03091008",
      "scene_id": "03091008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 71,
      "seq_in_scene": 71,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "奎顺"
      ],
      "text": "老伯饶命！",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03091008_e00072",
      "play_id": "03091008",
      "scene_id": "03091008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 72,
      "seq_in_scene": 72,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "陈荣"
      ],
      "text": "二相公哭得如酒醉，铁石人闻也泪抛。我本待将他释放了，陈贼知道怎肯饶！手执钢刀将他砍，他口口声声只叫饶。我还是杀的好放的好，倒叫老汉无计较。",
      "text_length": 69
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03091008_e00073",
      "play_id": "03091008",
      "scene_id": "03091008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 73,
      "seq_in_scene": 73,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "陈荣"
      ],
      "text": "也罢！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03091008_e00074",
      "play_id": "03091008",
      "scene_id": "03091008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 74,
      "seq_in_scene": 74,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "陈荣"
      ],
      "text": "宁可人头高杆吊，老汉放你去远逃！",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03091008_e00075",
      "play_id": "03091008",
      "scene_id": "03091008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 75,
      "seq_in_scene": 75,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "陈荣"
      ],
      "text": "二相公，老汉不杀你，放你逃走了吧！",
      "text_length": 17
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03091008_e00076",
      "play_id": "03091008",
      "scene_id": "03091008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 76,
      "seq_in_scene": 76,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "奎顺"
      ],
      "text": "谢老伯！",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03091008_e00077",
      "play_id": "03091008",
      "scene_id": "03091008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 77,
      "seq_in_scene": 77,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "奎顺下。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03091008_e00078",
      "play_id": "03091008",
      "scene_id": "03091008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 78,
      "seq_in_scene": 78,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "陈荣"
      ],
      "text": "走的好！",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03091008_e00079",
      "play_id": "03091008",
      "scene_id": "03091008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 79,
      "seq_in_scene": 79,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "奎顺上。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03091008_e00080",
      "play_id": "03091008",
      "scene_id": "03091008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 80,
      "seq_in_scene": 80,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "奎顺"
      ],
      "text": "走不得！文古贼子，重重禁门，叫我往哪里逃走！老伯，走不得！",
      "text_length": 29
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03091008_e00081",
      "play_id": "03091008",
      "scene_id": "03091008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 81,
      "seq_in_scene": 81,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "陈荣"
      ],
      "text": "二相公为何转来？",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03091008_e00082",
      "play_id": "03091008",
      "scene_id": "03091008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 82,
      "seq_in_scene": 82,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "奎顺"
      ],
      "text": "老伯，贼子重重禁门，我往哪里逃走！",
      "text_length": 17
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03091008_e00083",
      "play_id": "03091008",
      "scene_id": "03091008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 83,
      "seq_in_scene": 83,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "陈荣"
      ],
      "text": "呀！这贼子重重禁门，叫他往哪里逃走！哦，有了！二相公，马房后倒塌一垛土墙，老汉送你那里逃走了吧！",
      "text_length": 48
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03091008_e00084",
      "play_id": "03091008",
      "scene_id": "03091008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 84,
      "seq_in_scene": 84,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "奎顺"
      ],
      "text": "有劳老伯！",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03091008_e00085",
      "play_id": "03091008",
      "scene_id": "03091008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 85,
      "seq_in_scene": 85,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "陈荣"
      ],
      "text": "二相公不必泪嚎啕，老汉言来听根苗：遇着清官只管告，",
      "text_length": 25
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03091008_e00086",
      "play_id": "03091008",
      "scene_id": "03091008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 86,
      "seq_in_scene": 86,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "奎顺"
      ],
      "text": "老伯那厢有人！",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03091008_e00087",
      "play_id": "03091008",
      "scene_id": "03091008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 87,
      "seq_in_scene": 87,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "陈荣"
      ],
      "text": "什么人，待老汉看来！原来是系马的桩儿，待老扶助你一把。",
      "text_length": 27
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03091008_e00088",
      "play_id": "03091008",
      "scene_id": "03091008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 88,
      "seq_in_scene": 88,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "奎顺"
      ],
      "text": "高了上不去！",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03091008_e00089",
      "play_id": "03091008",
      "scene_id": "03091008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 89,
      "seq_in_scene": 89,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "陈荣"
      ],
      "text": "我找个石块垫着，二相公帮我一把！",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03091008_e00090",
      "play_id": "03091008",
      "scene_id": "03091008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 90,
      "seq_in_scene": 90,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "奎顺"
      ],
      "text": "哎呀！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03091008_e00091",
      "play_id": "03091008",
      "scene_id": "03091008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 91,
      "seq_in_scene": 91,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "陈荣"
      ],
      "text": "这做什么？",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03091008_e00092",
      "play_id": "03091008",
      "scene_id": "03091008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 92,
      "seq_in_scene": 92,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "奎顺"
      ],
      "text": "打了脚！",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03091008_e00093",
      "play_id": "03091008",
      "scene_id": "03091008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 93,
      "seq_in_scene": 93,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "陈荣"
      ],
      "text": "不要高声！",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03091008_e00094",
      "play_id": "03091008",
      "scene_id": "03091008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 94,
      "seq_in_scene": 94,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "陈荣"
      ],
      "text": "好与你父母把仇消。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03091008_e00095",
      "play_id": "03091008",
      "scene_id": "03091008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 95,
      "seq_in_scene": 95,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "奎顺上。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03091008_e00096",
      "play_id": "03091008",
      "scene_id": "03091008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 96,
      "seq_in_scene": 96,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "陈荣"
      ],
      "text": "走得好！一路之上，不知他可有盘费，待我叫他转来。二相公转来！",
      "text_length": 30
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03091008_e00097",
      "play_id": "03091008",
      "scene_id": "03091008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 97,
      "seq_in_scene": 97,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "奎顺"
      ],
      "text": "老伯，我走的好好，叫我转来何事？",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03091008_e00098",
      "play_id": "03091008",
      "scene_id": "03091008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 98,
      "seq_in_scene": 98,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "陈荣"
      ],
      "text": "你一路之上可有盘费？",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03091008_e00099",
      "play_id": "03091008",
      "scene_id": "03091008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 99,
      "seq_in_scene": 99,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "奎顺"
      ],
      "text": "老伯，我不过是求乞而已！",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03091008_e00100",
      "play_id": "03091008",
      "scene_id": "03091008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 100,
      "seq_in_scene": 100,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "陈荣"
      ],
      "text": "二相公，你乃读书之人，焉能作求乞之事？老汉有白银一锭，带在身旁，也好做个盘费！",
      "text_length": 39
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03091008_e00101",
      "play_id": "03091008",
      "scene_id": "03091008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 101,
      "seq_in_scene": 101,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "奎顺"
      ],
      "text": "老伯大恩，请上受我一拜！",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03091008_e00102",
      "play_id": "03091008",
      "scene_id": "03091008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 102,
      "seq_in_scene": 102,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "陈荣"
      ],
      "text": "不瞒你说，这银子不是我的，是陈碧桃陈小姐的。你要拜，看绣楼上有红灯一盏，你与她多拜几拜！",
      "text_length": 44
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03091008_e00103",
      "play_id": "03091008",
      "scene_id": "03091008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 103,
      "seq_in_scene": 103,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "奎顺拜，下。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03091008_e00104",
      "play_id": "03091008",
      "scene_id": "03091008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 104,
      "seq_in_scene": 104,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "陈荣"
      ],
      "text": "这一下脱了身，走得好！",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03091008_e00105",
      "play_id": "03091008",
      "scene_id": "03091008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 105,
      "seq_in_scene": 105,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "奎顺上。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03091008_e00106",
      "play_id": "03091008",
      "scene_id": "03091008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 106,
      "seq_in_scene": 106,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "奎顺"
      ],
      "text": "走不得，走不得！我走了不大要紧，陈文古向他要人，他把什么人交还？走不得！",
      "text_length": 36
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03091008_e00107",
      "play_id": "03091008",
      "scene_id": "03091008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 107,
      "seq_in_scene": 107,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "陈荣"
      ],
      "text": "为何又转来了？",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03091008_e00108",
      "play_id": "03091008",
      "scene_id": "03091008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 108,
      "seq_in_scene": 108,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "奎顺"
      ],
      "text": "老伯，我走了不大要紧，陈文古向你要人，你把什么人交还与他？",
      "text_length": 29
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03091008_e00109",
      "play_id": "03091008",
      "scene_id": "03091008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 109,
      "seq_in_scene": 109,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "陈荣"
      ],
      "text": "二相公，只要你脱身，休管老汉了！",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03091008_e00110",
      "play_id": "03091008",
      "scene_id": "03091008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 110,
      "seq_in_scene": 110,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "奎顺"
      ],
      "text": "老伯，我情愿一死，岂肯连累于你？将我杀了吧！",
      "text_length": 22
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03091008_e00111",
      "play_id": "03091008",
      "scene_id": "03091008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 111,
      "seq_in_scene": 111,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "陈荣"
      ],
      "text": "哎呀！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03091008_e00112",
      "play_id": "03091008",
      "scene_id": "03091008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 112,
      "seq_in_scene": 112,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "陈荣"
      ],
      "text": "好个有志奇男子，他比陈荣胜十分。世间多少男儿汉，要想比他万不能。",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03091008_e00113",
      "play_id": "03091008",
      "scene_id": "03091008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 113,
      "seq_in_scene": 113,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "陈荣"
      ],
      "text": "二相公，那厢有人来了！",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03091008_e00114",
      "play_id": "03091008",
      "scene_id": "03091008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 114,
      "seq_in_scene": 114,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "奎顺"
      ],
      "text": "在哪里？",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03091008_e00115",
      "play_id": "03091008",
      "scene_id": "03091008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 115,
      "seq_in_scene": 115,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "陈荣自刎。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03091008_e00116",
      "play_id": "03091008",
      "scene_id": "03091008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 116,
      "seq_in_scene": 116,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "奎顺"
      ],
      "text": "不好了！受我一拜！",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03091008_e00117",
      "play_id": "03091008",
      "scene_id": "03091008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 117,
      "seq_in_scene": 117,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "奎顺拜。",
      "text_length": 4
